    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607418478768423834)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRmjE95fD-_text","label":"ggRmjE95fD-_text","default":"<p>And it's already helping women just like yourself achieve things they never thought were possible:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_0","label":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_0","default":"<p>Sagging skin becoming dramatically firmer, with visible lifting results</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_1","label":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_1","default":"<p>Deep wrinkles and fine lines finally becoming noticeably smoother</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_2","label":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_2","default":"<p>\"Turkey neck\" and jowls visibly improving</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_3","label":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_3","default":"<p>It reduces firmness</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_4","label":"ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_4","default":"<p>Tired, aged appearance being replaced with a RADIANT glow...<br>the kind of youthful look you had decades ago, and the kind you can have again!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB9CIykbEL_text","label":"ggB9CIykbEL_text","default":"<p>And do you know what I love most about this formula?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHmfe-lTl7_text","label":"ggHmfe-lTl7_text","default":"<p>It's a non-surgical solution that doesn't require painful injections, expensive procedures, or risky operations of any kind.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWmsMNFMY3_text","label":"ggWmsMNFMY3_text","default":"<p>Our lab discovered a way to turn these ingredients – including the breakthrough peptide Progeline – into a single, powerful cream...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5sQtKn2G1_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg5sQtKn2G1_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-1xcEe7Zb_text","label":"gg-1xcEe7Zb_text","default":"<p>Our lab discovered a way to turn these ingredients – including the breakthrough peptide Progeline – into a single, powerful cream...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfz4oCnjhg_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggfz4oCnjhg_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRQaVoRpfN_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggRQaVoRpfN_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggs2obLP6iq_text","label":"ggs2obLP6iq_text","default":"<p>A cream you can apply yourself, every day, right in the comfort of your own home.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_grqFw2t9_text","label":"gg_grqFw2t9_text","default":"<p>And it goes to work tightening and firming your skin after just the very first use.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6YJF-YoSg_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg6YJF-YoSg_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/My_fine_lines_are_barely_visible_and_my_skin_looks_firmer_and_more_lifted._My_face_finally_looks_youthful_again_the_confidence_is_real._Elena_58_Verified_Vitro_Customer_1_copy-Photoro.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLKcWn-qRx_text","label":"ggLKcWn-qRx_text","default":"<p>Best of all, it has no harsh chemicals, no artificial ingredients, and none of the toxins found in most anti-aging products.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbachJNGIu_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggbachJNGIu_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx2img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbachJNGIu_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggbachJNGIu_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/My_fine_lines_are_barely_visible_and_my_skin_looks_firmer_and_more_lifted._My_face_finally_looks_youthful_again_the_confidence_is_real._Elena_58_Verified_Vitro_Customer_1_copy-Photoro.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqUpNPT80U_text","label":"ggqUpNPT80U_text","default":"<p>It's a healthy, dermatologist-formulated cream that is going to help you finally achieve the youthful appearance and confidence you DESERVE.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-BZyaKsND_text","label":"gg-BZyaKsND_text","default":"<p>I'm going to tell you exactly how you can get Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream in just a moment, but first, let me explain how we achieved these incredible results...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggr-Lm5M12B_text","label":"ggr-Lm5M12B_text","default":"<p>It's all thanks to these potent ingredients, which work because of what I call the<br>\"Anti-Progerin Complex”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmRsh0olZ5_text","label":"ggmRsh0olZ5_text","default":"<p>These four key ingredients work as a line of defense AND restore your skin from within:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcHDFG7Sab_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggcHDFG7Sab_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3licon1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrAZ1y_4XL_text","label":"ggrAZ1y_4XL_text","default":"<p>Progeline</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVsIPuaAq6_text","label":"ggVsIPuaAq6_text","default":"<p>Reduces aging Progerin levels by an astonishing 22%</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJeGNpx0-a_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggJeGNpx0-a_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3licon2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggC-6c6pY-G_text","label":"ggC-6c6pY-G_text","default":"<p>Matrixyl 3000</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg98HQ6wuQ-_text","label":"gg98HQ6wuQ-_text","default":"<p>Sends signals to replace lost collagen</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRPJ3xfNb2_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggRPJ3xfNb2_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3licon3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5Mfnronm-_text","label":"gg5Mfnronm-_text","default":"<p>Argireline</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj_mx-vatj_text","label":"ggj_mx-vatj_text","default":"<p>Helps prevent muscle movements that lead to wrinkles, like a gentle version of botox</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguM0-_YYoi_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gguM0-_YYoi_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3licon4.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYafxVdaqw_text","label":"ggYafxVdaqw_text","default":"<p>Ceramide</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQojZiHBlW_text","label":"ggQojZiHBlW_text","default":"<p>Holds these youth-boosting results together</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZxOkvOhUj_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggZxOkvOhUj_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2rwmhrbqK_text","label":"gg2rwmhrbqK_text","default":"<p>Of all the beneficial ingredients you can get into your skin, my favorite is Progeline by far.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggldaZDZrsJ_text","label":"ggldaZDZrsJ_text","default":"<p>That's because clinical studies have shown it to be effective in helping stop sagging, wrinkles, loss of firmness, and visible signs of aging.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglLQ1VcEHG_text","label":"gglLQ1VcEHG_text","default":"<p>It's also been shown to reduce the appearance of jowls and <strong>\"turkey neck.\"</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtH1IRtgXy_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggtH1IRtgXy_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbOQmGtgnd_text","label":"ggbOQmGtgnd_text","default":"<p>You see, most anti-aging treatments you see in stores or online are made with ingredients that can't penetrate deeply enough... the same problem we had with finding a Progerin solution.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXygygDQoz_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggXygygDQoz_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqOTnh48Db_text","label":"ggqOTnh48Db_text","default":"<p>So you'll see products advertised as having \"collagen\" or \"peptides\" or even \"stem cells\"...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDZwW4D6CO_text","label":"ggDZwW4D6CO_text","default":"<p>Sounds great! There's just one problem…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkEhJugkSs_text","label":"ggkEhJugkSs_text","default":"<p>If it's a cheap anti-aging cream, very few – or perhaps even NONE – of those beneficial ingredients will effectively penetrate the skin!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggebU32Pxyc_text","label":"ggebU32Pxyc_text","default":"<p>That's where our patented Anti-Progerin Complex comes in.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggT82sEpCug_text","label":"ggT82sEpCug_text","default":"<p>This advanced anti-aging formula is very unique. It has a sophisticated molecular structure that helps these compounds reach their cellular targets.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjAMBfigwJ_text","label":"ggjAMBfigwJ_text","default":"<p>In fact, these ingredients are specifically formulated to work at the deeper layers where Progerin accumulates!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOP9M0Vqql_text","label":"ggOP9M0Vqql_text","default":"<p>This is a MAJOR innovation in the field of anti-aging skincare, which is why I believe the clinical results have been so extraordinary.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwS7OnCGUt_text","label":"ggwS7OnCGUt_text","default":"<p>And it's in every jar of <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyE35Isi2M_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggyE35Isi2M_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/NoBotox_NoFiller_JustBalm._2_copy.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVRnK0JqCQ_text","label":"ggVRnK0JqCQ_text","default":"<p>But as I mentioned before, even the most powerful peptides would be useless without the right support ingredients... premium compounds that work together.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQrVcPjVe9_text","label":"ggQrVcPjVe9_text","default":"<p>And for Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream, I chose the most advanced peptides on the planet...</p>"}],
